Overview

[Rev 8:1](../../../bib/kjv/rev008.htm#001.md), At the opening of the
seventh seal, [Rev 8:2](../../../bib/kjv/rev008.htm#002.md), Seven angels
have seven trumpets given them; [Rev
8:6](../../../bib/kjv/rev008.htm#006.md), Four of them sound their trumpets
and great plagues follow; [Rev 8:9](../../../bib/kjv/rev008.htm#009.md),
Another angel puts incense to the prayers of the saints on the golden
altar.

